title: 'Star Wars: Rise of Skywalker': A Shocking Disappointment (SPOILERS) | The Watch
description:
If you liked 'Rise of Skywalker,' you're not going to like this podcast. The latest movie left us totally confused about where the franchise wants to go (4:15). We break down what worked and didn't work in the latest installment (23:35).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
